			<div class="content" id="post-content-4724858">
									

<p>So, when Parawatch was originally posted to the site, it said it was the Parawatch Wiki, but since then, we've gotten nothing but Parawatch Forums. This is an attempt to change that.</p>
<p>A rough template for the infobox, which is derived from the <a href="http://siliconcity.wikidot.com/template:villainbox">Silicon City wiki's villianbox template</a>, is here:</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
