<p>Since it relies on CSS, I can't demo it in the forum, but thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595479098" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;">stormbreath</a></span> for cleaning it up.</p>
<p>This template is just a starting point, and covers biographical and geographical data&#8212; you could put in things like historical events, if you really wanted. I know it looks complex, but it's not too too terrible, once you get the hang of it.</p>
<p>This is also intended as a tribute to the Magnus Archives, a horror podcast which has entered its final season earlier this year. In particular, the statement is meant as a tribute to it, and I'm hoping I at least competently emulated Jonathan Sims's writing style.</p>
<p>Image attribution:</p>
<p>The first image is from <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History_of_Poles_in_the_United_States#/media/File:Bronis%C5%82aw_Wilkoszewski_%E2%80%93_Fabryka_Tow._Ak._Pozna%C5%84skiego.jpg">here</a>, in the public domain. (Not putting raw URL due to text wrapping issues)</p>
<p>The second image is from: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_clock#/media/File:Time_clock_at_wookey_hole_cave_museum.JPG">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_clock#/media/File:Time_clock_at_wookey_hole_cave_museum.JPG</a></p>
<p>Also in the public domain.</p>
<p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1613974); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595479098" alt="UraniumEmpire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1613974); return false;">UraniumEmpire</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4558017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595479098" alt="Grigori Karpin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4558017)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;">Grigori Karpin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/barredowl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6001754); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6001754&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595479098" alt="barredowl" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6001754)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/barredowl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6001754); return false;">barredowl</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hexick" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5065702); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5065702&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595479098" alt="Hexick" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5065702)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hexick" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5065702); return false;">Hexick</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5336470); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5336470&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595479098" alt="cybersqyd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5336470)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5336470); return false;">cybersqyd</a></span>, and everyone else who critted this. Special thanks to <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Roger</span> Roget (freaking autocorrect) for creating Saltville way back in the SCP Origins RP, and UE for expanding on it. It's a setting which I might return to.</p>

